values: I'm sorry Folks . . .  sadly the Day has come that I make this Friends only instead of closeing it . . . too many people out there in the world looking to cause harm . . . If you are one of these people (And you know who you are) nice try but maybe you can get some Tips from your Momma on how to ruin peoples lives.

I'm going to a shrink tomorrow . . . thought I would never start an LJ entry like that.

But yea . . . basically the other person dosen't feel for me in the same way I felt for them . . . thats ok but now I feel like I'm 10,000 miles from them now.  All my friends in Lake View are fighting over Kim right now and I just don't know what to do with that and then theres ppl loseing babys and people hateing me and . . . yea . . . I'm preety much in need of a shrink . . . I want to cry but I physicall can't right now . . . I just hurt . . . I have noone to love me in the way I want to love someone . . . I just want a person that I know will be there for me untill I die . . . I want a soul mate damnit . . . I want a friend, a lover, a companion . . . I have friends but I will never trust them with secrets for the rest of my life . . . I just don't want to love anymore . . . I just want to go to a mountain and stand at its top and scream to the world that its not worth it anymore . . . I want to physically die.  I don't want to be here anymore . . . but I can't do that because others care about me.  I can't do it because I do have an undiscovered reason in this world . . . I've only loved 2 other ppl like I loved this person and I know from that that I will never stop loving them . . . 
 
 
I don't know why I post on here anymore . . . noone reads what I say.  Noone out there cares to read about me.  I'm goin to stop posting now.  Good life to everyone.

After a FuCkEd up X-mas season and alot of changes in my life . . . it feels so damn good to be back at Winthrop. Not sure yet but I think the infactuation has ceased to exist along with all of my other hopes of love . . . who needs that proverbial "Oxygen" when I have Helium . . . sorry had to be here to get that one . . . but yea . . . life is getting better . . . I EVEN BOUTE ME MYSELF AN IPOD WEDNESDAY Morning . . . but yea . . . Some things in the world are just hilarious like this website I created a few weeks ago (In honor of Russ) gokillyourself.bravehost.com . . . OMG I'm so mean but whatever . . . well let me go do a 15 min Walkthrew of this place . . . Take care all cows and remember to caio.

I think I'm in love . . . I haven't had feelings for a person like this in some time and I just can't believe it . . . the only problem is that the other person dosen't know . . . I THOUGHT I GOT OVER THIS CRUSHING SHIT A LONG TIME AGO . . . but yea . . . I just can't believe that love has shown its ugly pathetic face yet again in this little existance I live in called a world . . . its all confuseing to me . . . I just don't know what to do anymore . . . why is life so hard . . . why does life have to be this way . . . I'm not on trial . . . I'm not in tribulation . . . so WHY IN THE HELL DO I HAVE TO GO THREW THIS AGAIN!!!! . . .  Life is unfair . . . love is unfair . . . this world is unfair.  I think I need this break . . . I honestly need this break . . . I think I'm going psyco in this shell I live in called a body . . . I almost wish I could break out of it and be free but me as a human . . . I can't do that . . . I just don't understand anymore . . . life it such a bafle to me.  Existance is a way for some higher power to make fun at us . . . Why was I called into existance . . . what purpose do I serve on this powers playing field . . . I miss my old life in high school . . . everything was so easy then . . . all my friends . . . my world was Lake View and I didn't need anything else . . . but now that my world has expanded and I found this love . . . all I want to do is go crawl back up under my lil Lake View Rock and carry on existance in non-existance.  Well this my rant for the next few months . . . I'm gonna miss my love when they go home. . .  I don't know if I'll be able to survive without it.

I Am A: Chaotic Good Elf Bard Fighter

Alignment:
Chaotic Good characters are independent types with a strong belief in the value of goodness. They have little use for governments and other forces of order, and will generally do their own things, without heed to such groups.

Race:
Elves are the eldest of all races, although they are generally a bit smaller than humans. They are generally well-cultured, artistic, easy-going, and because of their long lives, unconcerned with day-to-day activities that other races frequently concern themselves with. Elves are, effectively, immortal, although they can be killed. After a thousand years or so, they simply pass on to the next plane of existance.

Primary Class:
Bards are the entertainers. They sing, dance, and play instruments to make other people happy, and, frequently, make money. They also tend to dabble in magic a bit.

Secondary Class:
Fighters are the warriors. They use weapons to accomplish their goals. This isn't to say that they aren't intelligent, but that they do, in fact, believe that violence is frequently the answer.

Deity:
Hanali Cenanil is the Chaotic Good elven goddess of love, beauty, and art. She is also known as the Heart of Gold and Lady Goldheart. Her followers delight in creation and youth, and work to spread happiness, love, and beauty. Their preferred weapon is the dagger.
